INSERT INTO `jobs` (`id`,`position_name`,`organization_title`,`organization_url`,`job_url`,`location`,`labor_function`,`posted_date`,`logo_url`,`description`) VALUES (68,'Senior Partnership Marketing Manager - Ecosystem Marketing','See more open positions at Gorgias','https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/gorgias-com#content','https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/gorgias-com/jobs/56168744-senior-partnership-marketing-manager-ecosystem-marketing','Toronto, ON, Canada','design',1754784000,'https://cdn.getro.com/companies/aecd14bd-7bf3-5c22-a035-772e03fc55bf-1747616949','<div> <div> <div> <h2>Location</h2> <p>Toronto</p> </div> <div> <h2>Employment Type</h2> <p>Full time</p> </div> <div> <h2>Department</h2> <p><span>Marketing</span></p> </div> <div> <h2>Compensation</h2> <ul><li><span>CA$120K – CA$140K</span></li></ul> <div> <p>Check the <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1wQ7EEMYSf06jYqoPx5-Pl6XMevSqJoLeJPU1Q5J_fxs/edit?gid=730598616#gid=730598616" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">public salary and equity calculator</a> to get the numbers tailored to your level and location. </p> <p><strong>Our calculator maintains fairness and pay equity within the organization, and you can</strong><a href="https://www.gorgias.com/blog/international-saas-salary-calculator" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow"><strong> find more info on how we calculate salaries here</strong></a><strong>.</strong></p> </div> </div> </div> <div> <div id="overview" aria-labelledby="job-overview" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0"> <div> <p>Gorgias is the conversational AI platform for ecommerce that drives sales and resolves support inquiries. Trusted by over 15,000 ecommerce brands, Gorgias supports growing independent shops to globally recognizable brands. </p> <p>Built for Shopify and powered by advanced ecommerce integrations, Gorgias''s conversational AI understands your brand, tools, policies, and customers to drive personalized, 1-to-1 conversations — from editing orders and initiating returns to making product recommendations. Gorgias, where every customer interaction feels personal, support becomes sales, and conversations shape success.</p>  <p><strong>About the Team</strong></p> <p>Gorgias is the leading CX platform for ecommerce, and the marketing team is a creative, technical, and revenue-driven crew focused on both short-term impact and long-term growth. With deep roots in conversational support and an expanding AI product suite, we’re entering a new era—bringing conversational AI to the entire customer journey. Our ecosystem of technology, agency, and referral partners plays a critical role in that transformation.</p> <p><strong>About the Role</strong></p> <p>We''re looking for a strategic and entrepreneurial <strong>Senior Manager, Ecosystem Marketing</strong> to lead partner marketing across our growing network of technology, agency, and referral partners—including Shopify, Recharge, Domaine, and Omnie. You’ll own the strategy and execution of co-marketing, enablement, and joint go-to-market programs that drive pipeline and revenue.</p> <p>Experience in the Shopify partner ecosystem is essential—but we’re not looking for rinse-and-repeat playbooks. We want someone ready to reimagine what ecosystem marketing can look like in 2025: high-trust, high-impact, and built on relationships in a changing marketing landscape.</p> <p>On the Gorgias marketing team, AI isn’t just a tool—it’s part of the org chart. We’re building marketing functions with AI agents as core teammates. If you''re excited to be a player-coach and know how to unlock leverage through automation and AI, you''ll thrive here.</p> <p>There’s headcount on the horizon, but the real growth opportunity is owning a high-impact charter at a pivotal moment—on a team driving innovation across programs, org design, and AI-native tooling.</p> <p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p> <ul> <li><p><strong>Pipeline Generation:</strong> Drive partner-sourced and partner-influenced pipeline growth through scalable joint go-to-market strategies—webinars, co-branded content, integrated campaigns, and partner events—with technology and agency partners at every tier.</p></li> <li><p><strong>Campaign Performance:</strong> Deliver measurable results from co-marketing and GTM efforts. Establish performance frameworks and reporting cadences that track impact from awareness through to closed-won revenue.</p></li> <li><p><strong>Partner Enablement:</strong> Equip partner sales teams with the tools, messaging, and programs needed to confidently position and sell Gorgias.</p></li> <li><p><strong>Team Development:</strong> Build and lead a high-performing (and AI-leveraged) ecosystem marketing team that scales with the business and amplifies broader marketing initiatives—from product launches to campaigns and events.</p></li> <li><p><strong>Strategic Partnerships:</strong> Deepen relationships with top partners through impactful collaboration. Stay on top of ecosystem trends and the evolving ecommerce partnership landscape.</p></li> </ul> <p><strong>Who You Are</strong></p> <ul> <li><p>5–7 years of experience in partner, channel, or product marketing, with a proven track record of scaling co-marketing programs across a variety of partner types.</p></li> <li><p>Deep experience in the ecommerce ecosystem, ideally within the Shopify partner landscape. Background with agency, referral, BPO, ISV, or TSD partners is a plus.</p></li> <li><p>An AI geek. You experiment constantly, test new tools, and can speak to how AI helps you move faster, better—not just for writing copy.</p></li> <li><p>Fluent in marketing systems: <a href="http://Customer.io" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">Customer.io</a> (or similar), HubSpot, Webflow, Splash. You don’t wait on others to get things launched.</p></li> <li><p>A storyteller who builds “1+1=3” partner narratives that stand out, drive enablement, and get results.</p></li> <li><p>Data-minded, with strong analytical skills to measure and optimize partner marketing performance.</p></li> <li><p>Collaborative and cross-functional—comfortable partnering with sales, product, and business development to make things happen.</p></li> </ul> <p><strong>Diversity &amp; Inclusion at Gorgias</strong><br>We celebrate diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive environment for all employees. We welcome applicants of all backgrounds, experiences, and perspectives. At Gorgias, we believe that diverse teams drive innovation and better decision-making. We do not discriminate based on race, color, religion, gender identity, sexual orientation, disability, age, or any other protected status.<br><br>If you need accommodations to participate in the application or interview process, perform essential job functions, or access other employment benefits, please contact us at <a href="#" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">accommodation@gorgias.com</a>. Let’s grow together!</p> <p>Compensation Range: CA$120K - CA$140K</p> </div> <a href="#"></a> </div> </div> </div>');
